There are many great things to do on the Upper Cape from fishing in the Cape Cod Canal to antiquing to dining out at some great Cape Cod traditional spots. There is parking all along the canal where you can drop a line right from the banks. There is also Route 6A in Sandwich, which has many antique shops that would take you an entire day to make it from one end to the other.
